-# Buttons -------------------------------------------------------------------
%p
  Button classes may be applied on <code>button</code> or <code>a</code> elements.
  %br
  As a convention, buttons should only be used for actions while hyperlinks are to be used for objects. For instance, <strong>"Download"</strong> should be a button while <strong>"recent activity"</strong> should be a link.

